      </p>
      
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-5">
        <a href="/WebsitePOT/contact" class="px-7 py-4 rounded-[6px] bg-[#E8593C] text-white font-[var(--font-body)] font-semibold text-lg hover:bg-[#cf4b31] transition-colors inline-flex items-center justify-center">
          Get Started — Free Consultation
        </a>
        <a href="/WebsitePOT/services" class="px-7 py-4 rounded-[6px] border border-[#F9FAFB] text-[#F9FAFB] font-[var(--font-body)] font-semibold text-lg hover:bg-[#F9FAFB] hover:text-[#1B3A5C] transition-colors inline-flex items-center justify-center">
          View Our Services
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
